{"tid":764803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[老老實實]作為香港人，唔理中國貨點樣都應該唱好！","createTime":"2018-08-02T09:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T21:02:22.000Z","uid":16562,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6c4e7092d68444a34837127aa43249357be181","tid":764803,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"講真，大陸人永遠都係對國貨冇乜信心先導致成日都落黎香港搶貨搞到百物騰貴。<br />\n當然，呢個係市場經濟原則，需求高自然物價貴，政府打住自由市場原則不干預係岩既。<br />\n<br />\n所以呀，我地作為香港人應該日日都幫中央政府唱好國貨增強內需，咁自然大陸民眾就會轉番去買番下國貨少啲黎香港買貨，自然香港貨價格會跌番去正常水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果咁都要屌我，咁即係你就係呢個潮流下既得利益者，例如疫苗公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唱好例子如下：<br />\n國產疫苗安全致上，國家級監管絕對有保證，目前事件只是孤立事件。<br />\n<br />\n國產奶粉品質優良，跟美國奶粉不會比下去，已從過去的錯誤中糾正。<br />\n<br />\n只要幫中央政府一把不停唱好國貨，對目前既高物價情況絕對有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63f12636a883dc5b07396c8faecf217c64473fb","tid":764803,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"咁快就比既得利益者負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a011ff6033c90a71d20783765c2e03ba404bdb","tid":764803,"uid":73439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"中國的五粮液 世界的 五粮液 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c5e60bb7abe3d89517eced6bc6b74b7bc9fd47","tid":764803,"uid":49588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"中國三鹿牌奶粉，是全世界最好嘅「奶粉」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6072730b69af361bd7fe35222779f9c8b9af2691","tid":7648